@cbillington @PhyNerd Thanks. I've updated the comment, description and removed the `clock_resolution` line \(I’ve left `clock_limit` there for now as it does actually do something…we possibly should make it configurable but Shaun and I have recently found that this can be difficult given the current labscript architecture, so something to fix in labscript v3\).

I also removed a couple of print lines I left in by mistake.
